-          <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem">
-            Structural Analogy (for clarity)
-          </p>
-          <p>
-            This system draws conceptual inspiration from the compiler engine of
-            <strong>Svelte</strong> — a modern JavaScript framework used in
-            front-end web development. But unlike most runtime systems, Svelte
-            pre-compiles behavioral logic at build-time.
-          </p>
-
-          <p>
-            Similarly, this strategic engine pre-encodes all consequences and
-            bypasses any post-hoc interpretation — including HR consulting or
-            legal reframing.
-          </p>
